  <summary date="2023-05-26T18:49:20Z" status="Introduced in House">Students Helping Young Students Act of 2023

This bill&#160;expands&#160;the federal work-study programs at&#160;institutions of higher education to include work-study programs that compensate students employed in the educational after-school, before-school, or out-of-school community service activities of public elementary or secondary schools.</summary>
